id hults patrick rp heller program on energy and sustainable development 2010 cover shifts in african crop climates by 2050 and the implications for crop improvement and genetic resources conservation marshall burke david lobell luigi guarino global environmental change 2009 cover nations states and violence david laitin oxford university press 2007 cover understanding the resource curse terry l karl open society institute in covering oil a guide to energy and development 2005 cover nigeria's struggle for democracy and good governance a festschrift for oyeleye oyediran abigun ab agbaje larry diamond ebere onwuiwe ibadan university press 2004 cover promoting real reform in africa larry diamond lynne rienner publishers in democratic reform in africa the quality of progress e gyimah boadi ed 2004 cover post communist paradox how the rise of parliamentarism coincided with the demise of pluralism in moldova eugene mazo cddrl working papers 2004 cover bottom of the barrel africa's oil boom and the poor ian gary terry l karl catholic relief services 2003 cover institutional design ethnic conflict management and democracy in nigeria rotimi suberu larry diamond oxford university press in the architecture of democracy constitutional design conflict mangement and democracy andrew reynolds ed 2002 previous records next records search fsi search within everything courses events fellowships news op eds people publications research other pages topical news pesd releases study of nigeria's national oil company nnpc september 10 2010 pesd announcement rising international stars 2010 draper hills summer fellows on democracy and development july 21 2010 cddrl fsi stanford draper hills summer fellows program announcement should oil producing countries emulate the norwegian model february 23 2010 pesd news ken banks on empowering grassroots movements using mobile technology november 5 2009 cddrl program on liberation technology news matt halprin and stephen king on using technology to c